## Data File Format

Generated data files are formatted in accordance with the Standard Time Series Data File Format. This file format has been developed to support [SAM](https://sam.nlr.gov/) and other NLR models and is documented fully in [this PDF](https://sam.nlr.gov/sites/default/files/content/documents/pdf/wfcsv.pdf). More information on SAM file formats available on [the SAM weather page](https://sam.nlr.gov/weather).

